title: Spacious & Bright Dog-Friendly One-Bedroom at East River Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '2320 Marshall Avenue - 411 | St. Paul, MN 55104', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available 10/1: Dog-friendly, modern apartment along the Mississippi River!', 'This corner apartment features an open floor plan with a spacious great room - perfect for hosting friends and family!', 'You will have access to your own private washer/dryer, a dishwasher, a moveable kitchen island, and an oversized bedroom.', 'The kitchen has granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.', 'Your many windows bring in an abundance of natural sunlight to illuminate your new home!', 'East River was built in 2014 and is conveniently located on the corner of Marshall & Otis in St. Paul.', 'Your new neighborhood is one block from the Mississippi River and across the street from the prestigious Town & Country Club.', 'The apartment views are breathtaking and include the Mississippi River bridge and Minneapolis skyline!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', "9' Ceilings", 'In-Unit Laundry', 'Dishwasher', 'Granite Countertops', 'Keyless Entry (FOBs)', 'Pet Friendly', 'Smoke-Free', '24/7 Emergency Maintenance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 643', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,437.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
